snippet: The young homeless man who accompanied Miley Cyrus to the MTV Video Music Awards arrived 45 minutes late for his arraignment Tuesday on a charge that he violated his probation in Oregon....

headline.print_headline: Miley Cyrus Date Barely Makes Court Appearance
headline.main: Miley Cyrus Date Barely Makes Court Appearance

lead_paragraph: The young homeless man who accompanied Miley Cyrus to the MTV Video Music Awards arrived 45 minutes late for his arraignment Tuesday on a charge that he violated his probation in Oregon.
